The opensource minimalist multi account twitter client for Chrome.

Just an alpha version, please don't expect more than it has.

With Twic now you can:
* Add as much accounts as you want
* Read the home timeline
* Write your tweets
* Reply (+ to all), retweet (+ oldscool), undo the retweet
* Delete your own tweets
* Get some info about user profile
* Follow/unfollow users

Changelog:
https://github.com/silentroach/twic/blob/master/Changelog

---

